## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d8ce3-109">다음 C# 코드를 사용 하 여 `GetNode` 노드에 액세스 하는 <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> 현재 배치 되어 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d8ce3-109">The following C# code uses `GetNode` to access a node the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> is currently positioned on.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XmlDocument doc = new XmlDocument();  
doc.Load("books.xml");  
XPathNavigator nav =  doc.CreateNavigator();  
XmlNode node = ((IHasXmlNode)nav).GetNode();  
Console.WriteLine(node.LocalName);   
//You can edit the returned XmlNode.  
```
